Package: guessMyLOI
Type: Package
Title: Guess Loss Of Imprinting
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Paolo Martini
Maintainer: Paolo Martini <paolo.cavei@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows the computation of Loss Of Imprinting.
  Moreover it contains specific functions for X Chromosome Inactivation detection.
  It also contains a shiny app.
License: AGPL-3
Depends: shiny, pheatmap, ggbio, ggplot2, GenomicRanges, RColorBrewer,
  VariantAnnotation, biovizBase, ggpubr
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
